    Serializable, Comparator<javax.mail.internet.InternetAddress>
    public class InternetAddressType
extends StringEncodedType<javax.mail.internet.InternetAddress>
    InternetAddress email address field type. Use requires javax.mail on the classpath.

    Null values are supported by this class.

    Note: the method InternetAddress.equals() performs a case-insensitive comparison of email addresses, ignoring the personal name, whereas this field type distinguishes instances that are not exactly equal.
